<plot>Tasha is a magical love story between a 14 year old boy from the city and a 14 year old girl from a small town. It's about those very first pangs of love where a simple kiss on the lips can amount to a taste and touch of heaven. And it's about how far a fragile insecure teenage boy is willing to go just to be accepted by the 'cool' kids, even rejecting the one true thing in his life... Tasha.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?531833</url></doc>
